{"tid":1992453,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"全球最大原油ETF急拋6月倉位！紐約期油跌破11美元","createTime":"2020-04-28T07:04:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T10:25:04.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a9afb2a20171fa92f652ac00fdfa9265cd072d17","tid":1992453,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:04:08.000Z","msg":"全球最大原油ETF急拋6月倉位！紐約期油跌破11美元<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3148010\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3148010&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPrZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=2b6c5de5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3148010&h=231e1b0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3148010</a><br />\n<br />\n〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕全球受疫情影響，原油需求大減，供需大亂之下，已經無處可儲放原油，加上全球最大石油ETF基金「美國石油基金（USO）」表示，將出售所有6月交割的原油期貨合約，使國際油價承壓，繼週一重挫近25％後，週二亞洲盤跌勢止不住，再挫15%。<br />\n<br />\n繼週一狂崩後，西德州中級原油（WTI）期貨價週二續跌15.3%，最低見每桶10.82美元，布蘭特原油期貨價亦挫3.8％；財經媒體「CNBC」報導，綜合各項預測，武漢肺炎疫情恐抹去全球高達1/3的原油需求，也使油價屢創低價紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n另外，全球最大石油ETF基金USO表示，將出售所有6月合約，並將移倉至遠月合約，這已是USO兩週內，第5次修改持倉策略；分析師指出，此舉代表USO看淡5月及6月的近月合約，儘管產油國協議減產，但由於需求降幅太大，許多人懷疑減產穩定市場的效果有限。"},{"pid":"3f788147ae436a073b43a56eb3a8fa88f7422b7a","tid":1992453,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:04:36.000Z","msg":"[行動po]香港人日程表更新<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1992311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1992311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"57b2d5823d382d648f4da134ec8ddac373bf3d0c","tid":1992453,"uid":217374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:06:44.000Z","msg":"Day low緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00cbe1fb3dbdfd6d2574be0308a628bd161a28b","tid":1992453,"uid":233237,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:16:01.000Z","msg":"3175完美避開，神操